{"tid":1913207,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"山寨版《瘟疫公司》成功在中國上架   《Virus Antidote 瘟疫解藥》抄足界面玩法","createTime":"2020-03-06T15:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T15:56:20.000Z","uid":104138,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09577726e8f088fc56b22c14e0e2f51bcfb20767","tid":1913207,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"早前曾經報導過中國國家網信辦以「存在違反國內法律內容」為由，將遊戲《瘟疫公司》（Plague Inc.）從中國 App Store 下架。近日發現有款與《瘟疫公司》類近的遊戲《疫情解藥─避免世界瘟疫末日》（Virus Antidote：Plague Cure）在中國 App Store 和各遊戲平台上架。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Screenshot-2020-03-06-at-3.20.13-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FScreenshot-2020-03-06-at-3.20.13-PM.png&h=c50a67ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據 App Store 和 Google Play 的資訊顯示，《疫情解藥─避免世界瘟疫末日》上架時間為 2 月 7 日，是由俄羅斯註冊的開發商 Action Portal 發行，無論是玩法、畫面、甚至是商標都與《瘟疫公司》幾乎相同，每週更要在 App 內收費港幣 110 元。<br />\n<br />\n這款遊戲和《瘟疫公司》的分別只是在於內容相反，《疫情解藥─避免世界瘟疫末日》的玩家需要研究入侵人類世界上的所有有害的病毒，找到對應的方法製作出相應的解藥來對抗病毒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Screenshot-2020-03-06-at-3.20.56-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FScreenshot-2020-03-06-at-3.20.56-PM.png&h=b75bf0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時《疫情解藥》的評分僅為 1 顆星，遭受網民負面評論。這次《瘟疫公司》被抄襲事件受到很多關注，也注意到北京當局的內容審查行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/06/virus-antidote/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F06%2Fvirus-antidote%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnJAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=4f4f1722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/06/virus-antidote/game-channel/</a><br />\n<br />\n只準中資上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845bf647e9173756b5b540b6bd4c438c76d81a27","tid":1913207,"uid":323443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"不意外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc975adb4f533b7f93213aaa8fc0f20415dc43c8","tid":1913207,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那中國造假最快手"},{"pid":"8754fc77a9f75b6c29c93c278a50418b9fea3869","tid":1913207,"uid":102835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">《疫情解藥─避免世界瘟疫末日》的玩家需要研究入侵人類世界上的所有有害的病毒，找到對應的方法製作出相應的解藥來對抗病毒</span><br />\n<br />\n政治正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲啲大陸仔AV都冇得睇"},{"pid":"badbdc4cd2c3cf04265f3c1246d01c3421c0eca5","tid":1913207,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8754fc77a9f75b6c29c93c278a50418b9fea3869","tid":1913207,"uid":102835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">《疫情解藥─避免世界瘟疫末日》的玩家需要研究入侵人類世界上的所有有害的病毒，找到對應的方法製作出相應的解藥來對抗病毒</span><br />\n<br />\n政治正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲啲大陸仔AV都冇得睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"不嬲都冇得睇啦"},{"pid":"36367e1a3ece437d2d1a795d493f2c622f1887bf","tid":1913207,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"有意思有意思"},{"pid":"4a9e741c6e1b8a595b15256cdfcf6dd253fffb0d","tid":1913207,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"原來將正版下架, 係為左俾自己人食左果浸錢<br />\n用政治鬥爭, 國家維穩角度去解讀支共, 唔一定中<br />\n用金錢利益去分析, 就一定無錯"},{"pid":"ed845e6590a3d2dfbce7c1f73ab94dc6766c7533","tid":1913207,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"即刻dl<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ndl黎負評同留言武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df4f95487863eafd1